{"tid":1384393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合][附英文信sample] 集體投訴紐西蘭嘅中國留學生打香港留學生","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T06:35:30.000Z","uid":282910,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"17d2d4f23ce53ddddbe3fde7a55e67bcfb8f4331","tid":1384393,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:33:50.000Z","msg":"原post﹕[突發］有巴絲打俾人放咗上微博！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382632/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382632/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片﹕<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wx9OgGDTNZM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dwx9OgGDTNZM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=e6c2fe76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wx9OgGDTNZM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n大頭﹕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWEG4DO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWEG4DO.png&h=e90e4b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巧京京，咁愛國嘅學生留係外國好危險，一定要快啲送佢返中國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生1: Edric Liu &lt; 推人果個，串過碼頭咕哩<br />\nfb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/edric.liu.77\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fedric.liu.77&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=8ad9db0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/edric.liu.77</a><br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/edricliu/?igshid=19co6ire9nxrq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fedricliu%2F%3Figshid%3D19co6ire9nxrq&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=c2889315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/edricliu/?igshid=19co6ire9nxrq</a><br />\n微博: <a href=\"https://sg.weibo.com/user/6088185581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsg.weibo.com%2Fuser%2F6088185581&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=74bf9378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sg.weibo.com/user/6088185581</a><br />\nHate Speech + Name calling + Woman Abuse <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學生2: Liu Renhe &lt; 鳩叫果個<br />\nfb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100009461833967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D100009461833967&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=96d03e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100009461833967</a><br />\nig: @liu.renhe<br />\n<br />\n學生3: Jianyu Zhao（好似係）&lt; 鬧英國人係豬果條友<br />\nig: @jianyu_zhao<br />\nHate Speech + Racist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投訢方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. Send email 去奧克蘭大學 University of Auckland <br />\ncity.security@auckland.ac.nz<br />\n2. Send email 去媒體 Stuff<br />\nnewstips@stuff.co.nz<br />\n3. 寄信Ministry of Business, Innovation and Employment，移民局係佢管，無得就咁send email去移民局<br />\ninfo@mbie.govt.nz.<br />\n4. Send email 去紐西蘭駐香港總領事館<br />\nnzcghkg@biznetvigator.com<br />\n5. 都可以去crimestoppers，但就麻煩啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crimestoppers-nz.org/about/contact-us/email-anonymously\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crimestoppers-nz.org%2Fabout%2Fcontact-us%2Femail-anonymously&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=f534a9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crimestoppers-nz.org/about/contact-us/email-anonymously</a>"},{"pid":"f04aa5fa6052d9d95e71c5718ae1f2e5f192a42a","tid":1384393,"uid":282910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:33:57.000Z","msg":"英文信sample<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（改自我係林卓廷？巴打。我改左一半左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當地人會用毛利文做信開頭，增加親切感。）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Concerning a recent conflict between students from Hong Kong and China in the University of Auckland</strong><br />\n<br />\nKia Ora,<br />\n<br />\nw <a href=\"http://ww.youtube.com/watch?v=wx9OgGDTNZM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dwx9OgGDTNZM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=97779aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ww.youtube.com/watch?v=wx9OgGDTNZM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\nI have recently come across a video clip of the above incident. As a Hong Kong citizen, I found it worrying as I know that there are a number of Hong Kong students studying in New Zealand and I would hate to see them to be the next victims.<br />\n<br />\nIn the incident, a group of international students from Hong Kong were trying to express their views on the recent protests in HK in a very peaceful manner. They put some post-its on a wall. Yet 3 Chinese male students came and started to call names. They called the girl &ldquo;a stupid pig&rdquo;, called British people &ldquo;Dogs&rdquo; (at 4:38) and even tried to assault the said girl later on.<br />\n<br />\nI know that New Zealand has a very diverse culture and kiwis are very peaceful people. Everyone should have their rights to express their political views and no one should be mistreated like this in New Zealand. <br />\n<br />\nI have no intention in interfering with the University&rsquo;s affairs, but I would hope the University to respond in a proactive manner to discourage such behaviour. <br />\n<br />\nCheers,<br />\n[YOUR NAME HERE]"},{"pid":"c9131de6d1f94836e9aa6aa3ef10ea9f13c64a33","tid":1384393,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"071042d8fe132be2a0f6da2ea841071b41262651","tid":1384393,"uid":70524,"like":1,"dislike":0